wiki.summary: “so american” was announced during the Chicago show of Olivia Rodrigo’s GUTS world tour during her performance of “get him back!”. It is the fifth and final bonus song included in the GUTS (spilled) deluxe, which released on March 22, 2024. The song is about her relationship with Louis Partridge, coming with the rumors, and this song giving them the place that they’re true. During the tracking week ending April 6, 2024, the song debuted at #58 on the Billboard Hot 100. Read more on Last.fm.
